{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTI2NjE0MDA1", "number": 65443, "title": "Send ban parent per outstanding child connection", "bodyText": "Few things that prevent us from supporting cross-clusters tasks cancellation:\n\n\nA child task gets canceled if a node with the parent task leaves the cluster. This doesn't hold for a cross-clusters task as the parent task does not belong to the remote cluster. This issue was resolved in #56620, where we cancel child tasks on disconnect instead.\n\n\nBan action isn't registered on proxy nodes\n\n\nBanned parent markers are removed when a node with the parent task leaves the cluster. This issue is similar to the first issue.\n\n\nThis commit tries to address the third issue by periodically (every 5 minutes) sending heartbeats for banned parent markers and removing markers that haven't received heartbeats for some time (30 minutes).\nThis commit tries to address the third issue by sending a ban for each outstanding child connection and removing it when all associated connections disconnect.", "createdAt": "2020-11-24T16:39:19Z", "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/65443", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "303b3c4961547ea47311236aa938ca0be0cf6182"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-12-08T16:55:04Z", "author": {"login": "dnhatn"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 13, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdfse0DAH2gAyNTI2NjE0MDA1OjFlMjYwMTE4ZjEyNGUxNTgwNzFjODIwYzExNmI5MjYxNzA5ZDFhZGE=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdkL7wWAH2gAyNTI2NjE0MDA1OjFjYWVkZjg0NWM1NWVhNmI2MGJiMTRkOTQ1MDI0M2RkOTQ3MDYxY2E=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "1e260118f124e158071c820c116b9261709d1ada", "author": {"user": {"login": "dnhatn", "name": "Nhat Nguyen"}}, "url": "https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/1e260118f124e158071c820c116b9261709d1ada", "committedDate": "2020-11-24T16:38:22Z", "message"